what_worked: Applied date_cte_isolate, dimension_cte_isolate, multi_date_range_cte: Isolated date filtering into a CTE, computed store-item revenue once in a CTE, then derived store averages from that CTE, eliminating duplicate fact table scans and enabling better filter propagation.
why_it_worked: Pre-filtering date dimension into CTE reduces hash join probe table from 73K to ~365 rows; Pre-filtering all dimension tables into CTEs avoids repeated full-table scans; Separate CTEs for each date alias avoids ambiguous multi-way date joins
